              "displayName": "Rohith Sharma K S",
              "active": true,
              "timeZone": "America/New_York"
            },
            "body": "Thinking instead of supporting new AM-RM IPC call, {{ApplicationMasterProtocol.registerApplicationMaster}} can be reused. Currently, on registration RM throws InvalidApplicationMasterRequestException. As a supporting updating web/rpc/trackingUrl , an update event to RMAppAttemptImpl can be send. But AM has to take descision whether to exit or continue running.",
